data.description: Your future home in the heart of Keller, nestled in one of DFW's most sought-after neighborhoods in a TOP-rated school district! This fabulous corner-lot home invites you to experience the suburban bliss amidst a rapidly growing area bursting with new shops, dining, & entertainment galore! Immaculate & meticulously maintained, this home displays timeless elegance & attention to detail at every turn. With elegant crown molding, rustic-style hard floors beautifully accentuating the white paneled cabinetry, a cozy fireplace, & playful pops of decorative lighting, this space is infused with character & warmth into every room. The covered back patio includes 2 ceiling fans and surrounded by lush, overgrown trees that offer both shade and privacy. Yop-rated schools, vibrant community parks, and just moments away from the bustling energy of Keller's newest hotspots, this home offers the ideal blend of tranquility and convenience. Get ready to make lasting memories in your new home-sweet-home!
